  "keyFeatures": [
    "16-week structured curriculum from basics to research-grade AI",
    "Zero-assumption math walkthroughs with step-by-step derivations",
    "Weekly coding challenges with starter code, tests, and reference solutions",
    "Multi-framework support (PyTorch, JAX, TensorFlow)",
    "Realm deep-dives for LLMs, vision, RL, multimodal, alignment, and interpretability",
    "Toy-safe defaults with explicit opt-in for large-scale training",
    "CLI tools for running experiments, tests, and quality checks",
